{"tid":159940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女司機油門當腳掣 鏟入舖撞飛執貨男","createTime":"2017-03-17T11:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T19:39:51.000Z","uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0adac606ae5c5f37d64382804fd063cc3d7085","tid":159940,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"上水發生驚險交通意外！下午4時許，一名38歲姓蘇的女子駕駛私家車由新成路的停車場駛出，其間疑誤油門當腳掣，導致私家車失控向前狂飆衝上新豐路，撞到一名正在舖外執貨的五金舖職員。24歲的五金舖職員頭、手、腳及腰部受傷，事後由救護車送往北區醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》事後取得一條事發時的閉路電視片段，顯示一名身穿綠色上衣的五金舖職員當時正在店外執貨，突然一輛私家車從後高速駛至，將他推前撞向舖面，幸當時並非「撞到應」，職員向前仆倒受傷，由途人扶走。五金舖東主聞聲走出店舖，發現私家車衝上行人路，隨即走前阻止，惟女司機疑驚魂未定，再誤油門當腳掣頭向前衝始停下。<br />\n<br />\n姓歐的五金舖東主事後表示，事發一刻他正在店內打電話，突然見到一輛私家車直衝店外，隨即跑出店外查看，發現其職員被撞。他指平日會將自己的客貨車停在舖前，惟今日有警察到場抄牌，於是將車駛走，詎料發生車禍，希望店員平安無事。"},{"pid":"b17025bea7f8bd63bc31b9ded373e2dac6698a6c","tid":159940,"uid":9899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:12:52.000Z","msg":"女司機"},{"pid":"3b4119d2b5a995a2592afec7fb2fb7a62feecbf6","tid":159940,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:15:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女司機</blockquote>"},{"pid":"afa591c42bb6405891cc9df6fc811bf96c83b3f0","tid":159940,"uid":26583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女司機</blockquote><br />\n入黎為左睇呢句"},{"pid":"04e89f96d5fb72694155fa4ad86192e07a03131a","tid":159940,"uid":60746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:18:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>女司機</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"07479a4e2e906a7104acba37fc43399855bffa27","tid":159940,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:18:53.000Z","msg":"點解女人會成日油門當腳掣？"},{"pid":"86a74479552a98b8993b104cbe4af0859fadb3de","tid":159940,"uid":19837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:20:13.000Z","msg":"連ＢＲＡＫＥ同ＡＣＣＥＬＥＲＡＴＥ都可以踩錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a030bbfba97a5f4b72c1456ca154a0e9d1785823","tid":159940,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連ＢＲＡＫＥ同ＡＣＣＥＬＥＲＡＴＥ都可以踩錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾油踩果個位<br />\n剎車又踩返果度？"},{"pid":"331c1ff860770e049b4dbe063c77d9ad5ba44eaa","tid":159940,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:23:32.000Z","msg":"留名睇絲打反駁男司機都會出意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c438a9291dc40663d6f3f01f10ae8eedd8242cd","tid":159940,"uid":2127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"公路炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907f75c83b723946b2564c4a84b7a34aee574881","tid":159940,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"仆你個街係鋪入面都比車撞"},{"pid":"b4db32a27fb5d9fa55a1ad1103df8ce06fcb0654","tid":159940,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:27:33.000Z","msg":"踩錯一下，之後俾人屌隻腳都唔轉再踩落去俾油？"},{"pid":"716a0abc15da912e162349bb7426a0d69c80d935","tid":159940,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>踩錯一下，之後俾人屌隻腳都唔轉再踩落去俾油？</blockquote><br />\n第一下意外 第二下謀殺？"},{"pid":"1e30e8f51230914db5a95d4ff925e738334b7f06","tid":159940,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"呀．．．．．．．．．．．．．"},{"pid":"1543333ca1a138b4791d18cb480aa02581abdfe1","tid":159940,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:00:16.000Z","msg":"女人揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df551dd6eb2197c89c3324d4801429622f2b187c","tid":159940,"uid":58254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime